ygData.msgSnippet: Heh I guess was funny though their is this real bad bard on E ci who is just a total jerk well he trained a couple groups almost got my gorup killed ticked me
ygData.messageBody:
Heh I guess was funny though their is this real bad bard on E'ci who is just
a total jerk well he trained a couple groups almost got my gorup killed
ticked me off so I dueled him while on my necro without pet. Was funny he
was stunned the whole fight and I had him dotted up while keeping him
stuned.

Naeeldar
